title: SA unbanned
subtitle: The judges have re-legalized the SA.
view-if: sa_banned == 1 and sa_ban_timer == 0 and full_reform_initiated = 1
on-arrival: sa_banned = 0; sa_strength += 110; sa_militancy += 0.05
tags: event

Judges have ordered the National Socialist SA to be re-legalized. They immediately return to mass recruiting and arming.
